title: NZD/USD Critical Near Term Downtrend Test Looms
text:
Fri, Jul 24, 2015, 6:04 AM AEST - Australia Markets open in 3 hrs 56 mins NZD/USD Critical Near Term Downtrend Test Looms By Jamie Saettele, CMT | DailyFX – 1 hour 24 minutes ago Recommend Automate trades with Mirror Trader and see ideas on other USD crosses -“A wedge may be underway from the February low though. The bearish pattern would complete on a break below the support line from that pattern.” The wedge target is .6607. -“The wedge objective has been reached as has the 2010 low at .6560. The next levels to be aware of are .64 (61.8% retracement of the 2009-2011 rally and 50% retracement of the 2000-2011 rally) and .60 ( long term double top target ).” A close above downtrend resistance (near .6720) is needed in order to indicate a larger reversal is underway.
